Thomas Sadoski https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Sadoski 0 Thomas Sadoski (born July 1, 1976) is an American stage, film, and television actor. He is best known for his roles as Don Keefer in the HBO series The Newsroom and as Matt Short in the sitcom television series Life in Pieces.
